Just for reference purpose, attaching the steps that we followed to create sandbox environment in UAT servers(10.10.10.10 ) 
It is presently pointing to DB 1.9.11.2:6603/uatldb
Server is running on 8743
logs available at /logs/jboss/pspa_sandbox/

1. /app/jboss/pspa_sandbox/logback-spring.xml
2. /app/jboss/pspa_sandbox/payment-api/
                paylahMq.properties
                sms.properties
                tigs.properties
                throttle.properties
3. /app/jboss/pspa_sandbox/bin/env.sh
                export API_LOG_CONFIG_HOME=$EAP_HOME/logback-spring.xml
                export JAVA_OPTS=" $JAVA_OPTS -Dlogging.config=$API_LOG_CONFIG_HOME"
                echo "API_LOG_CONFIG_HOME=$API_LOG_CONFIG_HOME"

4. /app/jboss/pspa_sandbox/configuration/standalone.xml
                                <datasource jndi-name="java:jboss/datasources/paylahDS" pool-name="paylahDS" enabled="true" use-java-context="true">
                                                <connection-url>jdbc:mariadb://10.91.110.20:6603/p2puatldb</connection-url>
                                                <driver-class>org.mariadb.jdbc.Driver</driver-class>
                                                <driver>MariaDB</driver>
                                                <pool>
                                                                <min-pool-size>20</min-pool-size>
                                                                <initial-pool-size>10</initial-pool-size>
                                                                <max-pool-size>50</max-pool-size>
                                                                <prefill>true</prefill>
                                                                <flush-strategy>InvalidIdleConnections</flush-strategy>
                                                </pool>
                                                <security>
                                                                <user-name>p2pdbadm</user-name>
                                                                <password>P2pdbadm#12</password>
                                                </security>
                                                <validation>
                                                                <check-valid-connection-sql>SELECT 1</check-valid-connection-sql>
                                                                <validate-on-match>true</validate-on-match>
                                                </validation>
                                </datasource>
                                                                                
                                <driver name="MariaDB" module="org.mariadb.jdbc">
                                                <xa-datasource-class>org.mariadb.jdbc.Driver</xa-datasource-class>
                                </driver>

5. Copy wmq directory to /opt/jboss/jboss-eap-7.0/modules/


6. /app/jboss/pspa_sandbox/deployments/paylahservice.war     

           
https://ip:8743/paylahservice/paylah/v1/purchase/payment

